<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="ko">
    <head>
        <meta charset="UTF-8"/>
        <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0"/>
        <title>EMA623_03_SU_0004_s</title>

        <!-- 공통 js-->
        <script src="../../common_contents/common/js/app.js"></script>

        <!-- 공통 css-->
        <link rel="stylesheet" href="./../../common_contents/common/css/app.css"/>

        <!-- 개별 -->
        <link rel="stylesheet" href="./../../common_contents/css/ema623_common.css"/>
        <link rel="stylesheet" href="./../../common_contents/css/ema623_03.css"/>
    </head>
    <body>
        <div id="app_wrap" class="ema623_03_SU_0004">
            <section class="title type2">
                <h2 data-head="2_pink" lang="y">쌓기나무로 만든 모양과 위에서 본 모양을 보고 쌓기나무의 개수를 알아봅시다.</h2>
            </section>

            <section class="contents paging_layout">
                <article class="page page_1">
                    <div class="img_row gap_32">
                        <div class="img_wrap">
                            <img src="../../common_contents/img/EMA623_03_SU/0004_img01.png" alt=""/>

                        </div>

                        <div class="input_area">
                            <div>
                                <h3 lang="y">위에서 본 모양을 보고 무엇을 알 수 있나요?</h3>
                                <div class="input_wrap">
                                    <math-field class="textarea"></math-field>
                                    <ol class="example_box">
                                        <li lang="y">바닥에 닿아 있는 면의 모양을 알 수 있습니다</li>
                                    </ol>
                                </div>
                                <p class="speech_bubble">바닥에 닿아 있는<br/>위에서 본 모양은 면의 모양과 같을까?
                                </p>
                            </div>
                        </div>
                    </div>
                </article>
                <article class="page page_2">
                    <div class="img_row building_blocks">
                        <div class="img_wrap">
                            <img src="../../common_contents/img/EMA623_03_SU/0004_img01.png" alt=""/>
                            <p class="diagram_green_tag" lang="y">위에서 본 모양</p>
                        </div>

                        <div class="input_area">
                            <div>
                                <h3 lang="y">쌓기나무로 똑같이 만들어 보세요.</h3>
                                <div class="gray_box">
                                    <div class="box_title">
                                        <button class="minus"></button>쌓기나무 개수<button class="plus"></button>
                                    </div>
                                    <div class="wood_box_area">
                                        <button class="wood_box"></button>
                                    </div>

                                </div>
                            </div>
                        </div>
                    </div>
                </article>
                <article class="page page_3">
                    <div class="img_row">
                        <div class="img_wrap">
                            <img src="../../common_contents/img/EMA623_03_SU/0004_img01.png" alt=""/>
                            <p class="diagram_green_tag" lang="y">위에서 본 모양</p>
                        </div>
                        <div >
                            <h3 lang="y">똑같은 모양으로 만드는 데 필요한 쌓기나무는 몇 개인가요?</h3>

                            <div class="question_box gap_8 justify_center">
                                <div class="input_wrap short_width">
                                    <math-field
                                        data-answer-single="10"
                                        placeholder="​"
                                        contenteditable="true"
                                        tabindex="0"
                                        id="page_4-math-field-3"
                                        sound="false"
                                        math-mode-space="\:"
                                        smart-fence="off"
                                        smart-superscript="off"></math-field>
                                    <div class="text_hint">10</div>
                                </div>
                                <span lang="y">개</span>
                            </div>
                        </div>
                    </div>
                </article>

                <div class="btn_area">
                    <button class="btnType key">입력타입토글</button>
                    <button class="btnReset">리셋</button>
                    <button class="btnCheck">확인</button>
                    <button class="btnSubmit">제출</button>
                </div>
            </section>
        </div>
    </body>
</html>